{"tid":336552,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企d甲由好痴線","createTime":"2017-07-26T13:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T15:53:36.000Z","uid":49480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4543eeb9b04af5ef3bf6642f3e16ee7ae219f65f","tid":336552,"uid":49480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T13:51:05.000Z","msg":"話說老母出遊都有一段時間<br />\n前排已經發現屋企多咗好多甲由bb<br />\n今日終於得閒買殺甲由藥放屋企<br />\n放好晒 就緊係拖下個地先啦<br />\n因為都好似幾污糟下<br />\n屌拿聲 個地都未拖完<br />\n拖完果d位即刻有甲由bb走出黎散步<br />\n仆你個街  我睇到起晒雞皮<br />\n到底點先可以徹底消滅佢地啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：勁驚甲由"},{"pid":"f978dcb631c9cb2516a3584e56c5a8de14ef3071","tid":336552,"uid":11420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T13:52:50.000Z","msg":"一點絕 我屋企本身好多<br />\n用完都有 不過眼見少左"},{"pid":"49d881118d6c9de3937bb88b366fb9fd63cde132","tid":336552,"uid":49480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T13:54:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一點絕 我屋企本身好多<br />\n用完都有 不過眼見少左</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n借問普通藥房有無得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e0c1e01dcb41dfd7d4d1fb112ca9cd63ceaf48","tid":336552,"uid":24948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T14:15:11.000Z","msg":"試下抺牆抺得乾淨啲 唔知甲由會唔會食上面啲油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e149a87011247f7d2b994254903c28b083b8dcf","tid":336552,"uid":49480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T14:57:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下抺牆抺得乾淨啲 唔知甲由會唔會食上面啲油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有大半個月無開爐煮野食"},{"pid":"f9cb8c8c006e9666d5879fff609504c332288410","tid":336552,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"